The 10 commandments
    1. Don't smoke. Never.
    2. Drink water (cold) or tea (warm) more then everything else.
    3. Drink alcohol moderate. Limited to social events. No drinking orgy.
    4. Breakfast. Lunch. Dinner. No overeating.
    5. Each day one pice of fruits.
    6. Eat meat moderte. Only high qualits meat.
    7. Eat fresh. Fresh vegetables.
    8. 10.000 steps a day. 5 hours sitting = 1 hour walking.
    9. Take the stairs. Always.
    10. No drungs. Never.
